I am fairly new to Practo  although I was getting my appointment alerts from this service for over a year. I realised it has all my appointment history from last one year with Dr. Rajan and I would like to say I strongly recommend his services. He has a very amicable and patient demeanour and is never in a hurry, unlike my previous dentists. The clinic is also very hygienic and the staff takes good care to maintain it that way. I got two of my teeth filled, one from Dr.Rajan and one from another dentist. The one he did is still in tact, while the other one has been causing me problems ever since, both done almost around the same time.  
All my life I have had bad dentists, and that even led to completely ignoring my dental health, refusing to visit a dentist, and did so only when it was strictly unavoidable. However, having moved from where I used to live, Dr. Rajan is no longer in an accessible distance  and  it is only fair to say that I have valued his services and thanks for the same. :)
